descriptionHtml:
Your new AA credit card app is now available.

With the app, you’ll be able to stay on top of your spending, search and tag transactions, and choose how you make payments. You can be reassured that your money is safe, with security features built-in as standard.

Here’s some of what you can expect:

SMART SEARCH
Search for and tag transactions by merchant and location.

SECURITY & FRAUD PROTECTION
Freeze and unfreeze your card in the app or on the website.
